  • Desktop: side-by-side layout (breakdown left, checkout right)
  • Trust badges: compact horizontal strip instead of 2x2 grid
  • Cleaner checkout button (no uppercase, no shadow)
  • Removed all gradient/glow clichés

  ============================================================================
